-- RBS May Pay Bankers Up to 2.5 Billion Pounds, Times Reports
-- B y   T u h i n   K a r
-- 2012-01-22T08:14:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-22/rbs-may-pay-bankers-up-to-2-5-billion-pounds-times-reports.html
Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc  may
pay investment bankers a total of about 2.5 billion pounds
($3.89 billion) including pay, perks and an estimated 500
million pounds in bonuses, the Sunday Times reported without
saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
